channel.description: The latest CVEs for SAP_SE -- SAPUI5 (PDFViewer)

item.title: CVE-2024-33007|2024-08-02T02:27:53.283Z -- sap_se -- sapui5%20%28pdfviewer%29
item.description: PDFViewer is a control delivered as part of SAPUI5 product which shows the PDF content in an embedded mode by default. If a PDF document contains embedded JavaScript (or any harmful client-side script), the PDFViewer will execute the JavaScript embedded in the PDF which can cause a potential security threat.
